node.text:
Barely graduated high school, community college drop out👇🏼

Family losses and poverty sent me down a 7 year path of alcohol and drugs in my 20s.👇🏼

After a failed suicide attempt at 25 I got 100% sober and learned one skill that sent my life on fire.👇🏼

I Learned how to buy and build companies.👇🏼

My first acquisition allowed me to position myself and acquire clients like LG, Pananasonic, Sony, Qualcomm, Google, Yahoo, Apple, Exxon Mobile and BP.👇🏼

1100 corporate clients in 30 months. I sold that company and used as a platform into the world of buying and selling companies.👇🏼

2 company exits one in 2014 and 2016.👇🏼

Built a 165 door real estate portfolio in 3 years. Debt free.👇🏼

16 7-8 figure acquisitions👇🏼

2 years on inc5000👇🏼

Follow me @kmallien to learn more about my story and how you can create the life you want👇🏼

@kmallien🔥
